Class GetAllUsersInEnterpriseRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.box.restclientv2.requestsbase.DefaultBoxRequest
      • com.box.boxjavalibv2.requests.GetAllUsersInEnterpriseRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBoxRequest

    public class GetAllUsersInEnterpriseRequest
extends DefaultBoxRequest
    Request to return Returns the list of all users for the Enterprise with their user_id, public_name, and login if the user is an enterprise admin. If the user is not an admin, this request returns the current user's user_id, public_name, and login.
